446
00:23:34,530 --> 00:23:37,950
Desmoronar, arder, por vossa causa!

447
00:23:44,623 --> 00:23:45,708
Obrigado.

448
00:23:46,709 --> 00:23:48,336
Vou segui-la.

449
00:23:48,419 --> 00:23:49,795
